## ─── Frontend environment variables ───────────────────────────────────────────
## Copy this to .env.local for local development (Vite reads .env.local).
## In production (Vercel), set these in the Vercel Dashboard → Settings → Environment Variables.

## Your deployed backend URL (Railway / Render / etc.)
## In development, leave blank — the Vite proxy handles /api automatically.
VITE_API_URL=https://your-backend.railway.app/api
